---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Programs" description="Learn about STEM+C's FIRST Robotics Competition (FRC) program and hands-on engineering education.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Programs</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 max-w-2xl">
        Real engineering. Real skills. Real impact.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Current Program: FRC -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-blue-600 text-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block bg-white/20 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4">
          Current Program
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">FIRST Robotics Competition (FRC)</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-blue-100 max-w-3xl">
          Our core program is FIRST Robotics Competition (FRC)—a high-energy, industry-grade engineering challenge where high school students design, build, program, and compete with full-sized robots in regional and national competitions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">More Than Building Robots</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            FRC is about much more than building robots. Students work in teams with professional mentors to develop skills in:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-blue flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Mechanical Design & CAD</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-blue flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>3D Printing & Assembly</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-blue flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Software Development & Control Systems</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-blue flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Project Management & Budgeting</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-blue flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Business Operations & Fundraising</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-blue flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Communication, Outreach, and Teamwork</strong></span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Join the Team</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            We are a <strong>community-based team</strong>, open to students from any school—or homeschool—in the greater Gilbert, Arizona area.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy mb-6">
            No experience required. Just curiosity, commitment, and a willingness to try (and sometimes fail).
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="bg-brand-purple text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-purple-900 transition-colors text-center">
              Join the Team
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Past Programs -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Past Programs</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
        Over the years, STEM+C has also participated in:
      </p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-2">FIRST LEGO League (FLL)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">2 seasons</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-2">FIRST Tech Challenge (FTC)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">7 seasons</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mt-8">
        These experiences helped us grow into the advanced FRC team we are today. Many of our alumni started in FLL or FTC before progressing into full-scale robotics and engineering careers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
